        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_ʒosæ" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>ʒosæ</orth></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>подливка</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>соус</q>
                        </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (раствор соли с кислым молоком,
                            чесноком, красным перцем и пр., в который макают хлеб, мясо)</note><note
                            type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (a sauce made of salt with sour milk,
                            garlic, red pepper, etc., in which bread, meat is
                    dipped)</note></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>xwærunmæ din kærʒin, ʒosæ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>для еды у тебя (есть) хлеб, соус</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>you (have) bread, sauce to eat</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Sozur"/><biblScope>19</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Родственно <mentioned xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>zōsa</w>
                        <gloss><q>род сиропа</q></gloss></mentioned>. Оба слова восходят к
                        <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/>
                        <w>*zauša-</w>
                        <gloss><q>нечто приятное, вкусное</q></gloss></mentioned>; ср. <mentioned
                        xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>ysua-(=*zūša-)</w>
                        <gloss><q>лакомство</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>ysōjsa-</w>
                        <gloss><q>вкусный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>ysūs</w>
                        <gloss><q>находить удовольствие в чем-либо</q></gloss></mentioned>,
                        <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>zaošā-</w>
                        <gloss><q>удовольствие</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"
                            ><w>zaoš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>иметь вкус к чему-либо</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>находить удовольствие в чем-либо</q></gloss></mentioned>,
                        <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>joṣa-</w>
                        <gloss><q>удовольствие</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                            ><w>juṣ-</w>
                        <gloss><q>пробовать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>отведывать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>вкушать с удовольствием</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>gustus</w>
                        <gloss><q>отведывание</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>вкушение</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
                            ><w>gustare</w>
                        <gloss><q>пробовать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>отведывать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>вкушать</q></gloss></mentioned> и пр. Для начального %iʒ%i (вместо
                    %iz%i) ср. такие дигорские формы, как %iʒæǧun%i (рядом с %izæǧun%i [см. <ref
                        type="xr" target="#entry_zæǧyn"/>] ‘сказать’, <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_ʒumarǧ"/> (из %izum-marǧ%i ‘горная индейка’ и др.) Сближение
                    с <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>yūš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>мясной навар</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>jūs</w>
                        <gloss><q>похлебка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>соус</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/>
                        <w>юха</w></mentioned> неприемлемо, так как начальный %iy%i не дает в
                    осетинском %iʒ%i.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"
                            /><biblScope>II 80, III 152</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">It is related with <mentioned xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>zōsa</w>
                        <gloss><q>a kind of syrup</q></gloss></mentioned>. Both words trace back to
                        <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/>
                        <w>*zauša-</w>
                        <gloss><q>something pleasant, delicious</q></gloss></mentioned>; cf.
                        <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>ysua-(=*zūša-)</w>
                        <gloss><q>dainty</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>ysōjsa-</w>
                        <gloss><q>delicious</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>ysūs</w>
                        <gloss><q>find pleasure in smth</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>zaošā-</w>
                        <gloss><q>pleause</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"
                            ><w>zaoš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>have taste in something</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>find pleasure in something</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>joṣa-</w>
                        <gloss><q>pleasure</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                            ><w>juṣ-</w>
                        <gloss><q>try</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>taste</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>taste with pleasure</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>gustus</w>
                        <gloss><q>tasting</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
                            ><w>gustare</w>
                        <gloss><q>taste</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>try</q></gloss></mentioned> etc. For the initial %iʒ%i (instead of
                    %iz%i) cf. such Digor forms as %iʒæǧun%i (and %izæǧun%i [see <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_zæǧyn"/>] ‘say’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ʒumarǧ"/>
                    (from %izum-marǧ%i ‘snowcock’ etc.) The connection with <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>yūš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>bouillon</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>jūs</w>
                        <gloss><q>slumgullion</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>соус</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/>
                        <w>юха</w></mentioned> is inappropriate because the initial %iy%i does not
                    reflet into %iʒ%i in Ossetic.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 80, III
                        152</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
            </entry>
